window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>After years of war, the necromancer Zaroth Karn finally lies dead at my feet, and I am one of the most powerful mages left standing.</p> <p>Now it’s time for peace—and to keep a promise to a fallen friend. He left me his quiet farmstead in the elven town of Aerenvale. With most men lost to the war, the women there could use a hand…or more.</p> <p>Time to hang up my artifact-level staff and battlemage armor, and to use my high-tier magic to create instead of destroy.</p> <p>Here's hoping the undead will stop bothering me....</p>"; 
